title: 1, 2, 3 Come to Pawleys Island with Me: A Beach Baby's First Counting Book
description: How many ways can you count how wonderful the beach is? In this beautifully illustrated book inspired by time spent on Pawleys Island, South Carolina, little ones are reminded of fun on the beach and taught the basics of counting to ten!
author: Annie Kelahan & Jared Smiley
